data.description: LOVELY UPGRADED MISSION VALLEY HOME. This corner lot home has it all. It has tiled floors throughout, 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 3-car garage, a spacious designer kitchen with lavish dark spacious cabinets. The appliances are black with stainless-steel which sit opposite the long kitchen island and breakfast bar. The expansive pantry was constructed for item easy to see and easy to reach. The living and dining areas are large, open, well laid out and just some of the things that set this floor plan apart. The master bedroom is sizable with an oversized linen closet, walk in closet, duel sinks and a walk-in shower. The indoor laundry room is enormous. The backyard is sizable, doesn't have neighbors behind the house but has a covered patio with seating area.
